---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<Header />
	<main>
		<!-- HERO SECTION -->
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-container">
				<div class="hero-image">
					<img
						src="/portrait-hero.jpeg"
						alt="Portrait"
						loading="eager"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="hero-text">
					<h1>
						You've built this level.<br />
						Now it's time to<br />
						embody the identity<br />
						that can hold the<br />
						next one.
					</h1>
					<div class="hero-details">
						<p>12-Month Private Advisory for high-performing entrepreneurs.</p>
						<p>Maximum 4 clients at a time.</p>
						<p>By application only.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="hero-divider"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 12-MONTH ADVISORY SECTION -->
		<section class="advisory">
			<div class="advisory-container">
				<div class="advisory-left">
					<h2>12-Month Private Identity &amp; Leadership Advisory</h2>
					<p>I work privately with a maximum of four leaders at a time.</p>
					<p>Over twelve months, we recalibrate identity, leadership and strategic direction to support your next level of power and responsibility.</p>
					<p>This is a confidential, high-touch advisory relationship — not coaching.</p>
					<a href="https://danitiavorswijk.satoriapp.com/offers/306908-alignment-session" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-outline">Request a Private Conversation</a>
				</div>
				<div class="advisory-right">
					<div class="criteria-block">
						<span class="criteria-label">THIS IS FOR YOU IF...</span>
						<ul>
							<li>You have built success, but feel internally misaligned with who you are becoming.</li>
							<li>You are ready to examine the identity that got you here — and rebuild for the next level.</li>
							<li>You seek depth over tactics, transformation over motivation.</li>
							<li>You are prepared to do the quiet, private work of recalibration.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="criteria-block">
						<span class="criteria-label">THIS IS NOT FOR YOU IF...</span>
						<ul>
							<li>You are looking for quick fixes or surface-level strategies.</li>
							<li>You are unwilling to examine your ego and its patterns.</li>
							<li>You prioritize comfort over growth.</li>
							<li>You are not ready to invest deeply in yourself.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- PRIVATE SURINAME IMMERSION SECTION -->
		<section class="immersion">
			<div class="immersion-container">
				<div class="immersion-image">
					<img
						src="/Private-Suriname-Immersion.jpg"
						alt="Suriname Immersion"
						loading="lazy"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="immersion-text">
					<h2>Private Suriname Immersion</h2>
					<span class="immersion-label">(INVITATION ONLY)</span>
					<p>Select clients may be invited to a private leadership immersion hosted in Suriname.</p>
					<p>A curated, 1:1 experience designed for deep integration and strategic recalibration.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="immersion-watermark">PRIVATE ADVISORY</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
		<section class="about">
			<div class="about-container">
				<span class="about-label">THE PATH IS THE CREDENTIAL</span>
				<blockquote class="about-quote">
					"They say the hardest battles are given to the strongest soldiers. I lived that truth."
				</blockquote>
				<div class="about-body">
					<p>For years, I walked the path of the "Black Sheep"; raising myself, navigating isolation, and fighting battles with no one to turn to. Paradoxically, while I struggled to find support for myself, I was always the anchor for everyone else.</p>
					<p>In the silence of that isolation, I wrestled with four questions:</p>
					<ul class="about-questions">
						<li>Why do I have to suffer?</li>
						<li>Why, despite everything, do I still have so much love to give?</li>
						<li>Why do I long for love, yet find it absent?</li>
						<li>Why must I fight so hard just to survive?</li>
					</ul>
					<p>I found the answers not in textbooks, but through the guidance of my ancestors; the Sáamaka Maroons of Suriname who fought for freedom and preserved their identity against all odds.</p>
					<p>Their wisdom taught me what no institution could: how to breathe through pain, how to journal my way to clarity, how to unlearn survival patterns and relearn thriving ones.</p>
					<p>I realized that my history was not a tragedy to overcome, but a curriculum to master. What I lived through does not make me a victim, it makes me a guide for those still on the journey. I have walked the path myself, and now I hold the lantern for leaders ready to find their own way.</p>
				</div>
				<span class="about-sacred">This is not coaching. This is sacred work, born from sacred wounds.</span>
				<p class="about-closing"><strong>You have built this level. Now let us build the identity that will hold the next one.</strong></p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- SÁAMAKA SOUL VISION SECTION -->
		<section class="vision">
			<div class="vision-container">
				<h2>The Sáamaka Soul Vision</h2>
				<span class="vision-label">FUTURE PROJECTS</span>
				<p>Sáamaka Soul is evolving into a broader leadership and cultural impact platform.</p>
				<p>Future projects include select intensives, legacy-driven initiatives and global collaborations rooted in identity, power and responsibility.</p>
				<span class="vision-link">Vision without noise.</span>
				<a href="https://danitiavorswijk.satoriapp.com/offers/306908-alignment-session" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-outline">Request a Private Conversation</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
	/* ========== HERO SECTION ========== */
	.hero {
		padding: 2rem 4rem 5rem;
	}

	.hero-container {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.hero-image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 600px;
		object-fit: cover;
		filter: grayscale(100%);
		display: block;
	}

	.hero-text h1 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 3.2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.hero-details p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.hero-divider {
		width: 40px;
		height: 1px;
		background-color: #333333;
		margin-top: 3rem;
	}

	/* ========== ADVISORY SECTION ========== */
	.advisory {
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.advisory-container {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 5rem;
	}

	.advisory-left h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.advisory-left p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #cccccc;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.btn-outline {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
		border: 1px solid #ffffff;
		color: #ffffff;
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.btn-outline:hover {
		background-color: #c9a227;
		border-color: #c9a227;
		color: #000000;
	}

	.criteria-label {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		color: #c9a227;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.criteria-block {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.criteria-block ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.criteria-block ul li {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #cccccc;
		line-height: 1.7;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.criteria-block ul li::before {
		content: '\00B7';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: #c9a227;
	}

	/* ========== IMMERSION SECTION ========== */
	.immersion {
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
		position: relative;
	}

	.immersion-watermark {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.6rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.25em;
		color: #a89060;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-align: right;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 2rem auto 0;
		opacity: 0.5;
	}

	.immersion-container {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.immersion-image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 500px;
		object-fit: cover;
		filter: grayscale(100%);
		display: block;
	}

	.immersion-text h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.immersion-label {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		color: #c9a227;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.immersion-text p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #cccccc;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	/* ========== ABOUT SECTION ========== */
	.about {
		padding: 6rem 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.about-container {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.about-label {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		color: #c9a227;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.about-quote {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin: 0 0 3rem;
		padding: 0;
		border: none;
	}

	.about-body p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #cccccc;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.about-questions {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 1.5rem 0 1.5rem 0;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.about-questions li {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #cccccc;
		line-height: 1.7;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.about-questions li::before {
		content: '\00B7';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: #c9a227;
	}

	.about-sacred {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #c9a227;
		display: block;
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.about-closing {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.about-closing strong {
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	/* ========== VISION SECTION ========== */
	.vision {
		padding: 6rem 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.vision-container {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.vision-container h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.vision-label {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		color: #ffffff;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.vision-container p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.vision-link {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: #ffffff;
		text-decoration: none;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		display: block;
		cursor: default;
	}

	.vision-container .btn-outline {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	/* ========== RESPONSIVE ========== */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 1rem 1.5rem 3rem;
		}

		.hero-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.hero-image img {
			height: 400px;
		}

		.hero-text {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.hero-text h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.hero-divider {
			margin-left: auto;
			margin-right: auto;
		}

		.advisory {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.advisory-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.advisory-left h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.advisory-left {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.btn-outline {
			display: inline-block;
		}

		.criteria-block {
			text-align: left;
		}

		.immersion {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.immersion-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.immersion-image img {
			height: 350px;
		}

		.immersion-text {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.immersion-text h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.about {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.about-quote {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.vision {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.vision-container h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.vision-container p {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
	}
</style>
